= MODULE

apache 

= DESCRIPTION

This is the apache module.
Manages apache servers, remote restarts, and mod_ssl, mod_php, mod_python, mod_perl

== Supported Platforms

* Debian
* Redhat and others: not  tested yet)

== Main classes

* apache($ensure) :: Install and configure apache

== Sample Usage

     import apache
     [...]
     class { 'apache':
           ensure => 'present'
     }

